BriefDescription: This event counts the woke event generated each time one of the woke condition occurs described in Arm Architecture Reference Manual for A-profile architecture. This event is only for output to the woke trace unit.

This event counts the woke event generated each time an event is counted by an event counter <n> and all of the woke condition occur described in Arm Architecture Reference Manual for A-profile architecture. This event is only for output to the woke trace unit.
